{"title":"喂，当你想放弃了就来看看","date":"2019-10-07T02:04:14.000Z","thumbnail":"/2019/10/07/wuhan/12.jpg","link":"2019/10/07/wuhan","tags":["生活"],"updated":"2019-10-07T14:36:40.268Z","content":"  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>国庆假期本来是安安心心在自习室复习准备明年考研的，之前的同学叫我去武汉，其实心中一直对武汉大学憧憬，这也算是我来武汉的初衷吧</p>\n<h2 id=\"武汉大学\">武汉大学<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#武汉大学\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"牌坊\">牌坊<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#牌坊\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/42.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/13_3.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"校训\">校训<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#校训\"></a></h3><p>进门就是武大的校训了~ </p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/43.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"计算机学院\">计算机学院<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#计算机学院\"></a></h3><p>作为一名程序员，有什么景色都先不管，肯定要去人家的计算机学院啦~ 羡慕， 自己要是能去就好了~ </p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n152.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>可惜没去成人家图书馆，学校实在大旁边的那两个走不动啦~</p>\n<h3 id=\"校园骑行\">校园骑行<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#校园骑行\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n1.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"博物馆\">博物馆<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#博物馆\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n2.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"鉴湖\">鉴湖<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#鉴湖\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n4.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"樱花大道\">樱花大道<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#樱花大道\"></a></h3><p>可惜这个时间没有樱花</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n5.JPG\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"樱园\">樱园<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#樱园\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n6.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n7.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n8.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"樱园宿舍\">樱园宿舍<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#樱园宿舍\"></a></h3><p>貌似是博士生才能住的宿舍，环境优美~ </p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n9.JPg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n10.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n1512.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"樱园上方的城堡\">樱园上方的城堡<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#樱园上方的城堡\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n11.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n12.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n163.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n164.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n16.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n1511.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"梅园操场\">梅园操场<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#梅园操场\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n13.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n14.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/13_2.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n154.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"珞珈山\">珞珈山<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#珞珈山\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n155.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"月湖\">月湖<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#月湖\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n156.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"其他\">其他<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#其他\"></a></h3><p>这张就像电影里的那种感觉~  很惬意</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n151.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"东湖\">东湖<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#东湖\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n153.JPG\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/10/07/wuhan/n157.jpg\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\">总结<a href=\"2019/10/07/wuhan#总结\"></a></h2><p>武大的校园氛围给人莫名的舒适，自由。武大很美，但是真正对我很大感触并不在此，而在于—当我骑上车想到能够 在这种氛围下，骑着车和几个挚友谈谈心，排解排解压力，谈谈生活，一起为课业忙碌，拼搏， 一起因为那些烦恼而忧虑，一起为生活奋斗，其实这就是我心中的那份美好吧，我一直所追求的。说实话，上了三年大学，这是我人生中第一次在大学的校园骑车，直到那一刻我真正明白努力生活的意义，我也明白自己真正想要的是什么，为了心中的那份美好吧。此刻，我望着车窗也许是不舍、是悔恨、是不甘……. 耳机响着音乐，此刻，我对着屏幕记录，眼角湿润，这一次，积压在我心中的泪再也不想忍了…….</p>\n","prev":{"title":"10.7打卡","link":"2019/10/07/new/107"},"next":{"title":"10.2打卡","link":"2019/10/02/new/102"},"plink":"http://zqynn.github.io/2019/10/07/wuhan/","toc":[{"title":"武汉大学","id":"武汉大学","index":"1","children":[{"title":"牌坊","id":"牌坊","index":"1.1"},{"title":"校训","id":"校训","index":"1.2"},{"title":"计算机学院","id":"计算机学院","index":"1.3"},{"title":"校园骑行","id":"校园骑行","index":"1.4"},{"title":"博物馆","id":"博物馆","index":"1.5"},{"title":"鉴湖","id":"鉴湖","index":"1.6"},{"title":"樱花大道","id":"樱花大道","index":"1.7"},{"title":"樱园","id":"樱园","index":"1.8"},{"title":"樱园宿舍","id":"樱园宿舍","index":"1.9"},{"title":"樱园上方的城堡","id":"樱园上方的城堡","index":"1.10"},{"title":"梅园操场","id":"梅园操场","index":"1.11"},{"title":"珞珈山","id":"珞珈山","index":"1.12"},{"title":"月湖","id":"月湖","index":"1.13"},{"title":"其他","id":"其他","index":"1.14"},{"title":"东湖","id":"东湖","index":"1.15"}]},{"title":"总结","id":"总结","index":"2"}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://zqynn.github.io/2019/10/07/wuhan/\" title=\"喂，当你想放弃了就来看看\">http://zqynn.github.io/2019/10/07/wuhan/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}